stlib.interfaces.unit.spatial.util

Interface MovableFaceIF

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MovableSpatial
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MovableFace

    public interface MovableFaceIF
extends MovableSpatial
    Interface for MovableFaceIF objects, which are generally used to build 'UnitRegionIF' objects.
    This objects can have moving holes.
    Author:
    Markus Fuessel
